slides.title: Associations
slides.text: when looking at the associations we see two groupings, in the upper left we have groups like "Stop-hinkley"  and "No to new nuclear" in the bottom right we have groups like "Foratom" and "World Nuclear.

slides.title: Industry
slides.text: if we add industry sites to the map, we see they are all clustered in the bottom right, these are sites like "EDF" and "Horizon nuclear"

slides.title: Private actors
slides.text:
if we remove industry and instead add the private actors they are all clustered in the top left 

this shows us that spilt between what associations private actor and industry refer to
